data.description: Enjoy the serenity of nature from the comfort of your own home with this cozy residence. The 1-story layout and 3 bedrooms & 2 baths provides easy access and ample space for all. Upon entering the home, you'll be greeted by a spacious entry foyer that provides convenient built-in storage and hangers to help you stay organized. The large open island kitchen is a chef's dream, complete with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances that make meal preparation a breeze. Ceiling fans in every bedroom and living room ensure your comfort throughout the year, while the 2-car garage with epoxy floor and automatic garage door openers provide easy and secure access to your vehicles. Big fenced backyard with peaceful view. Plenty of amenities to keep you active and entertained, including a beautiful lake, park, neighborhood pool, and clubhouse. If you are looking for a beautiful country setting in a quiet gated community, this home is sure to fit the bill.
